2009 ANU Student Union President Sham Sara discusses the first annual ANU End of Year Festival was held on the Chifley Library lawns on Sunday 22 November.The event featured Gorman House Markets, live music, a jumping castle, super slide, face painting, roving circus performers, gourmet food stalls and sideshows.
